snippet.title: BIFROST SPIRE - PlayStation GalaTrailer [HD]
snippet.description:
Bifrost Spire second Trailer. A Cooperative Bullet-Hell Twin-Stick Shooter. Play as a Viking on his quest to climb a tower filled with bullets and become a god of Valhalla. Bifrost Spire is currently in development by Pink Dogs and powered by GameNest.

Game developer: Luis Monteiro 
2D Artist: Aquiles dias, Wendy Agostinho
Game designer: João Inez 
3D Artist: Ruben Teixeira 
Sound Designer: Tomas
